  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if a program of physical activity, nutritional
      supplements and relaxation techniques is effective at decreasing post operative complications
      in frail colorectal cancer patients undergoing resection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
